%20the%20statement%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20collegium%20system%20has%20many%20flaws.%20It%20is%20undemocratic.%20It%20has%20shut%20the%20doors%20of%20judgeship%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20on%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20even%20the%20poor%20among%20the%20upper%20castes%2C%26quot%3B%20claimed%20Mr%20Kushwaha%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Morcha%20(RLM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20bench%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20high%20courts%2C%20it%20is%20dominated%20by%20members%20of%20a%20few%20hundred%20families.%20A%20reason%20why%20the%20anomalous%20system%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20no%20less%20than%20the%20current%20president%20and%20her%20predecessor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kushwaha%2C%20who%20was%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20HRD%20in%20the%20first%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20recalled%20the%20National%20Judicial%20Appointments%20Commission%20Bill%20which%20was%20brought%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20reason%2C%20it%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20RJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20the%20NDA%20partner%20questioned%20his%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20justice%20credentials%26quot%3B%2C%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bhe%20had%20been%20a%20Union%20minister%20and%20an%20important%20ally%20of%20the%20UPA%20for%20the%20entire%20period%20the%20Congress-led%20coalition%20in%20power.%20But%20never%20did%20he%20raise%20a%20voice%20against%20the%20collegium%20system%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20corruption%20scandals%20against%20the%20RJD%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Kushwaha%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20cannot%20expect%20a%20principled%20stand%20on%20such%20issues%20from%20someone%20who%20keeps%20oscillating%20between%20jail%20and%20bail%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20NDA%20that%20dared%20to%20bite%20the%20bullet%20on%20the%20thorny%20issue%20of%20collegium%20system.%20And%20it%20is%20the%20NDA%20which%20will%20continue%20to%20make%20efforts%20in%20this%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Kushwaha%20has%20been%20a%20votary%20of%20reservations%20in%20higher%20judiciary%20and%2C%20despite%20switching%20allies%20a%20number%20of%20times%2C%20has%20not%20diluted%20his%20stand%20on%20the%20contentious%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OBC%20leader%20also%20bristled%20at%20%26quot%3Brumours%20spread%20by%20detractors%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20had%20opposed%20the%2010%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20introduced%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20supported%20the%20bill.%20If%20anybody%20can%20show%20any%20evidence%20that%20I%20had%20opposed%20it%2C%20I%20will%20retire%20from%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20apparently%20wary%20of%20an%20upper-caste%20backlash%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20is%20scheduled%20in%20Karakat%20on%20June%201%20and%20Mr%20Kushwaha%20is%20locked%20in%20a%20three-cornered%20contest%20with%20Raja%20Ram%20of%20CPI(ML)%20Liberation%20and%20Bhojpuri%20superstar%20Pawan%20Singh%20who%20is%20contesting%20as%20an%20Independent%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20into%20a%20sizeable%20share%20of%20Rajput%20votes%20despite%20expulsion%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716718740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2F0p04sgr4_upendra-kushwaha-pti_625x300_30_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-led-nda-will-try-to-scrap-undemocratic-collegium-system-ex-union-minister-upendra-kushwaha-5749246%