d%20Ukraine.%20In%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fetc-corporate.org%2Fnews%2Feuropes-tourism-displays-a-strong-rebound-but-remains-uneven-across-the-regions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20European%20Travel%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20COVID-19%20brought%20tourism%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20countries%20closest%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20the%20Baltic%20region%2C%20have%20been%20the%20slowest%20to%20recover%20pre-pandemic%20tourism%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20here%20are%20five%20European%20countries%20that%20Abbamonte%20said%20offer%20fewer%20crowds%20and%20more%20perks%2C%20including%20yummy%20food%2C%20beautiful%20architecture%2C%20and%20stunning%20scenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20if%20you've%20already%20booked%20your%20trip%20to%20Spain%2C%20Italy%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20France%2C%20he%20highlighted%20some%20hidden%20gem%20spots%20off%20the%20beaten%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20more%20to%20Romania%20than%20meets%20the%20eye%2C%20according%20to%20Abbamonte.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sunny%20day%20at%20Mamaia%20beach%20in%20Romania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647ab9820abc1efe8fb44f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20people%20mistakenly%20assume%20that%20Romania%20is%20landlocked%2C%20Abbamonte%20said.%3Cp%3ECalin%20Stan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20recommends%20only%20a%20brief%20pit%20stop%20in%20Romania's%20capital%2C%20Bucharest%2C%20before%20driving%20through%20%26quot%3Bawesome%26quot%3B%20regions%20like%20Transylvania%2C%20known%20for%20storied%20castles%20and%20medieval%20villages%20lined%20with%20cobblestone%20streets%20like%20Brasov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20road%20trip%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20p