%20told%20BI%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funder-the-radar-islands-everyone-should-visit-in-their-lifetime-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflies%20under%20the%20radar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you%20visit%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20Abbamonte%20advised%20skipping%20Prague%20and%20making%20a%20beeline%20for%20smaller%20villages.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20town%20of%20%C4%8Cesk%C3%BD%20Krumlov%20by%20a%20river%20and%20surrounded%20by%20trees%20and%20hills.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647ac0514fb5b23cc5df6af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C4%8Cesk%C3%BD%20Krumlov%20is%20a%20lesser-known%20city%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20than%20Prague.%3Cp%3EPetr%20Polak%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Abbamonte%20said%20Prague%20is%20one%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bfavorite%20cities%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20that%20to%20truly%20appreciate%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20%E2%80%94%20which%20most%20Czechs%20call%20Czechia%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20cool%20stuff%20outside%20Prague%20to%20see%2C%20and%20most%20people%20never%20leave%20the%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Romania%2C%20Abbamonte%20added%2C%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bawesome%26quot%3B%20place%20to%20take%20a%20road%20trip%20through%20many%20picturesque%20villages%20and%20small%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20go-to%20stops%20is%20%C4%8Cesk%C3%BD%20Krumlov%2C%20known%20for%20its%20medieval%20architecture%2C%20river%2C%20and%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPoland%20is%20beautiful%20and%20chock-full%20of%20'life-altering'%20historic%20sites%2C%20he%20said.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22927%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krak%C3%B3w%2C%20Poland%20with%20views%20of%20the%20Vistula%20River%20and%20Wawel%20Castle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647ac8814fb5b23cc5df6f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPoland%20is%20brimming%20with%20history.%3Cp%3EMichal%20Krakowiak%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Abbamonte's%20experience%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20Americans%20sleep%20on%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Eastern%20European%20country%20is%20worth%20visiting%2C%20he%20said%2C%20to%20explore%20urban%20areas%20like%20the%20river-side%20city%20Krakow%20and%20the%20port%20city%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGdansk%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20capital%2C%20Warsaw%2C%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Brebuilt%26quot%3B%20after%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20also%20said%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20and%20emotional%20experiences%20people%20can%20have%20in%20Poland%20is%20touring%20concentration%20camps%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauschwitz-photos-nazi-camp-history-liberation-anniversary-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAuschwitz-Birkenau%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20life-altering%20stuff%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20relatives%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20half%20Jewish%2C%20so%20it%20was%20really%20striking%20for%20me%20to%20be%20there%20knowing%20that%20some%20of%20my%20relatives'%20descendants%20fled%20to%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESerbia%20is%20worth%20a%20trip%20for%20its%20capital%2C%20Belgrade%2C%20alone%2C%20Abbamonte%20feels.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20harbor%20in%20Belgrade%20at%20dusk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647acf114fb5b23cc5df724%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20vibrance%20of%20Belgrade%20defied%20Abbamonte's%20expectations.%3Cp%3Emareandmare%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20entire%20Balkan%20region%2C%20which%20includes%20Bosnia%2C%20Montenegro%2C%20Slovenia%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Serbia%20stands%20out%20to%20Abbamonte%20because%20he%20finds%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Belgrade%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20the%20singular%20most%20underrated%20city%20in%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20expectations%20of%20an%20Eastern%20European%20city%20that%20has%20experienced%20so%20much%20violence%20in%20recent%20history%20were%20not%20high%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20you%20get%20there%2C%20and%20it's%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20right%20on%20the%20river%2C%20it%20has%20great%20restaurants%2C%20a%20great%20bohemian%20scene%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20coffee%20shop%2C%20and%20bars.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20night%2C%20the%20city%20truly%20comes%20alive%2C%20Abbamonte%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20turns%20into%20this%20raging%20nightlife%20place%2C%20and%20it's%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerbia%20also%20has%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20mountain%20towns%2C%26quot%3B%20Abbamonte%20added%2C%20which%20offer%20more%20chances%20to%20meet%20friendly%20and%20insightful%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20the%20whole%20country%20to%20be%20fascinating%20and%20the%20people%20to%20be%20interesting%20because%20they%20have%20dealt%20with%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAbbamonte%20tells%20people%20to%20seek%20out%20hidden-gem%20spots%20within%20heavily%20touristy%20countries%20including%20Spain%2C%20Italy%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20France.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowded%20street%20in%20Santorini%2C%20Greece%20(Left)%20and%20a%20quiet%20street%20in%20Aegina%2C%20Greece%20(Right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647b18420abc1efe8fb48f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbbamonte%20suggests%20swapping%20popular%20destinations%20for%20lesser-known%20ones%2C%20like%20choosing%20the%20Greek%20island%20of%20Aegina%20over%20the%20more%20common%20destination%20of%20Santorini.%3Cp%3Embbirdy%2FGetty%20Images%2C%20zoom-zoom%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20also%20has%20plenty%20of%20off-the-beaten-path%20tips%20for%20the%20handful%20of%20countries%20he%20calls%20the%20Big%20Four%3A%20France%2C%20Spain%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20booked%20to%20go%20to%20France%20this%20summer%2C%20he%20recommended%20visiting%20Biarritz%2C%20a%20coastal%20town%20close%20to%20the%20border%20with%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20only%20French%20people%20go%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20why%20I%20like%20it%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%20has%20a%20real%20local%20old-money%2C%20Grace%20Kelly%20kind%20of%20feel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Spain%2C%20one%20of%20Abbamonte's%20favorite%20places%20to%20visit%20is%20A%20Coru%C3%B1a%2C%20a%20port%20city%20in%20northwest%20Galicia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20beautiful%20coastal%20town%20that%20nobody%20goes%20to%2C%20and%20it's%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20also%20suggested%20checking%20out%20the%20smaller%20Italian%20villages%20of%20San%20Gimignano%20and%20Montalcino.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20Lake%20Como%20experience%2C%20he%20added%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20lakes%20in%20the%20Dolomite%20Mountains%20that%20are%20just%20as%20beautiful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Greece%2C%20Abbamonte%20said%20Meteora%20in%20Thessaly%20is%20%26quot%3Botherworldly%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20monasteries%20perched%20on%20rock%20cliffs%2C%20and%20US%20tourists%20sleep%20on%20a%20northern%20city%20called%20Thessaloniki.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20have%20never%20been%20there%20or%20have%20ever%20heard%20of%20it%20or%20can%20spell%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20cool%20city%2C%20pretty%20cheap%2C%20and%20interesting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreek%20islands%2C%20he%20recommended%20Hydra%2C%20which%20is%20quiet%20and%20car-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20goats%2C%20donkeys%2C%20and%20walking%2C%26quot%3B%20Abbamonte%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20cool%20place%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funderrated-european-countries-for-summer-travel-better-than-tourist-favorites-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716717121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6650cfbb20abc1efe8fd8280%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funderrated-european-countries-for-summer-travel-better-than-tourist-favorites-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lee%20Abbamonte%20said%20most%20Americans%20overlook%20Eastern%20Europe%2C%20which%20has%20beautiful%20architecture%2C%20vibrant%20restaurants%2C%20and%20unspoiled%20natural%20beauty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funderrated-european-countries-for-summer-travel-better-than-tourist-favorites-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%2C%20Suhana%2C%20AbRam%20jet%20off%20for%20IPL%20finals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716716915000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110438414%2Cimgsize-40252.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhi