3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20conversation%20with%20a%20former%20associate%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%20They%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20due%20to%20privacy%20concerns.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20their%20identity%20and%20employment%20at%20McKinsey.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-consulting-firm-boost-morale-eminem-bob-marley-internal-event-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassociate%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20almost%20two%20years.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20McKinsey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-consultant-layoffs-firing-over-hiring-client-demand-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehired%20too%20many%20consultants%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20overestimating%20the%20market.%20It%20was%20tough%20to%20get%20on%20projects%2C%20but%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20on%20four%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eduring%20my%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20performed%20well%20in%20my%20first%20year%20and%20never%20received%20any%20negative%20feedback.%20I%20was%20told%20my%20performance%20was%20above%20the%20bar%20at%20my%20first%20review.%20My%20higher-ups%20supported%20my%20presence%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20and%20my%20clients%20were%20happy%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20my%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20next%20review%2C%20six%20months%20later%2C%20things%20completely%20changed.%20I%20was%20put%20on%20%26quot%3Bconcerns%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rating%20McKinsey%20gives%20to%20consultants%20whose%20performance%20it%20deems%20unsatisfactory.%20I%20was%20told%20I'd%20have%20six%20months%20to%20improve%20or%20be%20put%20on%20track%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20gave%20me%20vague%20reasons%20for%20my%20rating.%20I%20was%20told%20I%20wasn't%20taking%20%26quot%3Bend-to-end%20ownership%26quot%3B%20of%20projects%20and%20implementing%20%26quot%3Btop-down%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20hard%20to%20develop%20within%20a%20year%20of%20joining%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20job.%20In%20previous%20years%2C%20if%20you%20had%20been%20put%20on%20%26quot%3Bconcerns%2C%26quot%3B%20they'd%20try%20to%20find%20work%20to%20help%20you%20improve%2C%20but%20the%20firm%20explicitly%20said%20they%20would%20not%20help%20me.%20It%20was%20clear%20they%20just%20wanted%20people%20to%20leave.%20Just%20two%20months%20after%20I%20received%20the%20rating%2C%20I%20left%20and%20started%20looking%20for%20another%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3f22847-9cfc-4e50-9209-734640dffa63%5C%22%3EMcKinsey's%20shadow%20followed%20me%20on%20my%20job%20search%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20performance%20rating%20impacted%20my%20job%20search%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird-party%20recruiting%20agencies%20asked%20me%20for%20my%20rating.%20I%20also%20contacted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-top-priority-ceos-going-into-next-year-mckinsey-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%20alumni%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20a%20job%2C%20and%20some%20asked%20me%20for%20my%20rating%20up%20front.%20The%20minute%20my%20interviewers%20found%20out%20I'd%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Blow-performer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20dynamic%20of%20the%20interview%20process%20completely%20changed.%20They'd%20low-ball%20salary%20offers%20because%20they%20knew%20people%20like%20me%20needed%20a%20job%2C%20and%20we%20weren't%20just%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20from%20our%20current%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-consultant-quit-mental-health-shattered-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20health%20also%20took%20a%20huge%20hit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20was%20reflected%20in%20my%20interviews.%20McKinsey%20hires%20overachievers%2C%20so%20it's%20tough%20to%20project%20confidence%20when%20you're%20told%20you're%20a%20low%20performer.%20I%20couldn't%20leave%20my%20house%20for%20months%20and%20I%20kept%20agonizing%20over%20how%20to%20land%20my%20next%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20get%20on%20many%20projects%2C%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20build%20my%20skill%20set.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20justify%20to%20potential%20employers%20why%20I%20should%20be%20hired%20into%20a%20better%20position.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20worried%20that%20I'd%20have%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20and%20accept%20a%20lower%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20almost%20five%20months%20to%20land%20another%20job.%20I'm%20happy%20with%20my%20new%20role%20even%20though%20I%20had%20to%20take%20a%2020%25%20pay%20cut.%20But%20my%20advice%20to%20McKinsey%3A%20Just%20do%20layoffs%20so%20your%20former%20employees%20don't%20need%20to%20explain%20themselves%20so%20much%20in%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMcKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20consultant%20who's%20being%20haunted%20by%20a%20bad%20performance%20review%3F%20We%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Contact%20reporter%20Lakshmi%20Varanasi%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Alvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Elvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-jobs-performance-rating-layoffs-job-search-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716716822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664fa82c239fda2da6cb3b3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-jobs-performance-rating-la