A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20for%20the%20entire%20country%20will%20be%20implemented%20within%20the%20next%20five%20years%20after%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20if%20the%20BJP%20returns%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20its%20next%20term%20will%20also%20implement%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20as%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20the%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20simultaneously%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20further%20said%20the%20simultaneous%20elections%20will%20also%20bring%20down%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20moving%20elections%20to%20winter%20or%20some%20other%20time%20of%20the%20year%20as%20against%20the%20current%20one%20being%20held%20in%20scorching%20heat%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20think%20over%20it.%20If%20we%20prepone%20one%20election%2C%20it%20can%20be%20done.%20It%20should%20be%20done.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20time%20of%20students'%20vacation.%20It%20creates%20lots%20of%20problems%20too.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20election%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20gradually%20moved%20to%20this%20period%20(during%20summer).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20UCC%20is%20a%20responsibility%20left%20to%20us%2C%20our%20Parliament%20and%20the%20state%20legislatures%20of%20our%20country%20since%20independence%20by%20the%20makers%20of%20our%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guiding%20principles%20decided%20for%20us%20by%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20include%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%20And%20even%20at%20that%20time%2C%20legal%20scholars%20like%20K%20M%20Munshi%2C%20Rajendra%20Babu%2C%20Ambedkar%20Ji%20had%20said%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20laws%20based%20on%20religion%20in%20a%20secular%20country.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20done%20an%20experiment%20in%20Uttarakhand%20where%20it%20has%20a%20majority%20government%20as%20it%20is%20a%20subject%20of%20states%20and%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%20has%20been%20on%20the%20BJP's%20agenda%20since%20the%201950s%20and%20recently%20it%20was%20enacted%20in%20BJP-ruled%20Uttarakhand.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20a%20huge%20social%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20religious%20reform.%20The%20law%20made%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20should%20undergo%20social%20and%20legal%20scrutiny.%20Religious%20leaders%20should%20also%20be%20consulted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20mean%20is%20that%20there%20should%20be%20an%20extensive%20debate%20on%20this.%20And%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20to%20change%20in%20the%20model%20law%20made%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20after%20this%20extensive%20debate.%20Because%20someone%20will%20definitely%20go%20to%20court.%20The%20judiciary's%20opinion%20will%20also%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20the%20state%20legislatures%20and%20Parliament%20of%20the%20country%20should%20think%20seriously%20over%20this%20and%20a%20law%20must%20be%20enacted.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20written%20in%20our%20'sankalp%20patra'%20that%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20have%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20for%20the%20entire%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20it%20can%20be%20done%20within%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20it%20will%20be%20done%20in%20this%20period%20only.%20%26quot%3BFive%20years%20are%20a%20sufficient%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20also%20make%20every%20effort%20to%20achieve%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'.%20This%20should%20also%20be%20discussed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20formed%20the%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20committee.%20I%20was%20also%20a%20member%20of%20it.%20Its%20report%20has%20been%20submitted.%20The%20time%20has%20come%20that%20elections%20should%20be%20held%20simultaneously%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20a%20bill%20on%20this%20can%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20next%20session%20if%20the%20BJP%20returns%20to%20power%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20resolution%20is%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20will%20bring%20it%20during%20this%20period.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20said%20that%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Constitution%20lists%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20as%20one%20of%20the%20Directive%20Principles%20of%20State%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20believes%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20gender%20equality%20till%20such%20time%20Bharat%20adopts%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20which%20protects%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20women%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20reiterates%20its%20stand%20to%20draw%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20drawing%20upon%20the%20best%20traditions%20and%20harmonising%20them%20with%20the%20modern%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20manifesto%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%2C%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-powered%20Committee%20to%20examine%20the%20issues%20of%20conducting%20simultaneous%20elections%20and%20it%20will%20work%20towards%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20make%20provisions%20for%20a%20common%20electoral%20roll%20for%20all%20levels%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20head