The%20department's%20proposal%20received%20a%20flood%20of%20negative%20comments%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fago.mo.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024-5-16-Student-Loan-NPRM-Interested-States-Comment-Letter.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2020%20Republican%20state%20attorneys%20general%20who%20claimed%20the%20relief%20is%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20least%20the%20American%20people%20should%20be%20able%20to%20expect%20is%20that%20people%20receiving%20debt%20cancelation%20actually%20apply%20for%20it%20and%20that%20the%20Department%20makes%20a%20determination%20on%20an%20individual%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20the%20Department%20is%20twisting%20the%20law%20to%20forgive%20as%20many%20loans%20as%20possible.%20This%20is%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20attorneys%20general%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-save-plan-lawsuit-gop-attorneys-general-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20filed%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20block%20some%20of%20Biden's%20more%20targeted%20relief%20efforts%2C%20like%20relief%20through%20the%20new%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%2C%20and%20it's%20highly%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-new-student-loan-forgiveness-plan-be-blocked-scotus-chevron-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20will%20arise%3C%2Fa%3E%20once%20the%20administration%20gets%20closer%20to%20finalizing%20this%20new%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20maintained%20confidence%20in%20the%20legality%20of%20its%20relief%2C%20vowing%20to%20move%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20so%20borrowers%20can%20start%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20day%20one%20of%20my%20Administration%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20fight%20to%20ensure%20higher%20education%20is%20