s%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibtimes.co.in%2Findian-origin-researcher-finds-way-charge-car-10-minutes-revolutionise-ev-future-868461%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20IANS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20new%20technology%20has%20been%20discovered%20by%20Ankur%20Gupta%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20chemical%20and%20biological%20engineering%20at%20the%20US-based%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder%20and%20his%20team%20of%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Proceedings%20of%20the%20National%20Academy%20of%20Sciences%2C%20researchers%20discovered%20the%20movement%20of%20ions%E2%80%94tiny%20charged%20particles%E2%80%94within%20a%20complex%20network%20of%20microscopic%20pores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Mr%20Gupta%2C%20the%20development%20of%20more%20efficient%20storage%20devices%20like%20supercapacitors%20can%20be%20accelerated%20by%20this%20breakthrough%20discovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20mentioned%20that%20a%20supercapacitor%20is%20an%20energy%20storage%20device%20that%20depends%20on%20ion%20collection%20in%20their%20pores.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20in%20comparison%20to%20batteries%2C%20supercapacitors%20have%20fast%20charging%20times%20and%20longer%20life%20spans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assistant%20professor%20noted%20that%20this%20discovery%20is%20crucial%20not%20only%20for%20storing%20energy%20in%20EVs%20and%20electronic%20devices%20but%20also%20for%20power%20grids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20power%20grids%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%20that%20fluctuating%20energy%20needs%20efficient%20storage%20to%20avoid%20waste%20during%20periods%20of%20low%20demand%20and%20ensure%20speedy%20delivery%20during%20periods%20of%20high%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20researchers%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20primary%20appeal%20of%20supercapacitors%20lies%20in%20their%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20said%20that%20in%20just%20minutes%2C%20this%20discovery%20allows%20the%20simulation%20and%20prediction%20of%20ion%20flow%20in%20a%20complicated%20network%20of%20thousands%20of%20interconnected%20pores.%20They%20explained%20that%20before%20this%20discovery%2C%20the%20movements%20of%20ions%20were%20only%20defined%20in%20the%20literature%20in%20one%20straight%20pore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphys.org%2Fnews%2F2024-05-laptop-minute-supercapacitors-clues.html%5C%22%3EPhys.org%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20Ankur%20Gupta%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20energy%20in%20the%20future%20of%20the%20planet%2C%20I%20felt%20inspired%20to%20apply%20my%20chemical%20engineering%20knowledge%20to%20advancing%20energy%20storage%20devices.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20topic%20was%20somewhat%20underexplored%20and%2C%20as%20such%2C%20the%20perfect%20opportunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20appeal%20of%20supercapacitors%20lies%20in%20their%20speed.%20So%20how%20can%20we%20make%20their%20charging%20and%20release%20of%20energy%20faster%3F%20By%20the%20more%20efficient%20movement%20of%20ions.%20That's%20the%20leap%20of%20the%20work.%20We%20found%20the%20missing%20link.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716714960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ft2i3a8jg_electric-car_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-researcher-discovers-way-to-charge-laptops-in-a-minute-and-cars-in-10-minutes-5748555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20researcher%20and%20his%20team%20have%20unveiled%20a%20novel%20technology%20that%20can%20charge%20an%20electric%20car%20in%2010%20minutes%20and%20a%20dead%20laptop%20and%20phone%20in%20a%20minute.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-researcher-discovers-way-to-charge-laptops-in-a-minute-and-cars-in-10-m