E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20his%20shot%20selection%20had%20been%20good%2C%20his%20India%20career%20too%20would%20have%20been%20long.%20I%20hope%20that%20the%20opportunity%20he%20has%20got%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20he%20grabs%20it%20with%20both%20hands%20and%20cements%20his%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20legend%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Samson%20has%20found%20a%20place%20in%20the%2015-member%20India%20squad%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant%2C%20who%20has%20also%20made%20it%20to%20the%20squad%20as%20another%20wicketkeeper-batter%20in%20the%20team%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20India's%20first%20choice%20in%20the%20tournament.%20This%20means%20that%20Samson%20will%20either%20get%20no%20or%20very%20limited%20chances%20in%20the%20T20%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716711840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fe1sqoc2o_sanju-samson-bcci_625x300_25_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwhy-has-sanju-samson-not-had-a-steady-india-career-sunil-gavaskars-brutal-assessment-5744020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20cricketer%20was%20left%20fuming%20over%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Sanju%20Samson%20during%20Qualifier%202%20of%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwhy-has-sanju-samson-not-had-a-steady-india-career-sunil-gavaskars-brutal-assessment-5744020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwhy-has-sanju-samson-not-had-a-steady-india-career-sunil-gavaskars-brutal-assessment-5744020%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwhy-has-sanju-samson-not-had-a-steady-india-career-sunil-gavaskars-brutal-assessment-5744020%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGrew%20Up%20Washing%20Cups%20And%20Plates%20As%20A%20Child%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20At%20Mirzapur%20Rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20grew%20up%20washing%20cup%20plates%20and%20serving%20tea%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20Modi%20and%20tea%20is%20very%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20washing%20cups%20and%20plates%20as%20a%20child.%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20serving%20tea.%20The%20relationship%20between%20Modi%20and%20tea%20is%20also%20very%20deep%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Mirzapur%C2%A0today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20wants%20to%20waste%20their%20vote%20on%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20No%20one%20will%20vote%20for%20someone%20who%20is%20drowning.%20The%20common%20man%20will%20vote%20only%20for%20the%20one%20whose%20government%20is%20certain%20to%20be%20formed.%20The%20country%20has%20come%20to%20know%20the%20people%20of%20the%20INDI%20alliance%20very%20well.%20These%20people%20are%20deeply%20communal.%20These%20people%20are%20extreme%20casteists.%20These%20people%20are%20extreme%20familyists.%20Whenever%20their%20government%20is%20formed%2C%20these%20people%20take%20decisions%20on%20this%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20promising%20people%20in%20the%20Yadav%20community%20but%20he%20(Akhilesh)%20gave%20tickets%20only%20to%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20SP%20people%20used%20to%20release%20even%20those%20terrorists%20who%20were%20caught.%20The%20SP%20government%20used%20to%20suspend%20any%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20reluctant%20in%20this.%20They%20had%20made%20the%20entire%20UP%20and%20Purvanchal%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20mafia.%20Be%20it%20life%20or%20land%2C%20no%20one%20knew%20when%20it%20would%20be%20snatched%20away%20and%20in%20the%20SP%20government%2C%20the%20mafia%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20asserted%20that%20CM%20Yogi%20is%20carrying%20forward%20the%20'Swachhta%20Abhiyan'%20very%20bravely.%20The%20public%20was%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20SP%20government%20but%20now%20the%20mafia%20is%20trembling%20in%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sacred%20Constitution%20of%20our%20country%20is%20also%20on%20their%20(INDI%20alliance)%20target.%20They%20want%20to%20loot%20the%20reservation%20of%20SC-ST-OBC.%20Our%20Constitution%20clearly%20says%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20had%20released%20its%20manifesto%20during%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20elections%20in%202012.%20Then%20SP%20had%20said%20in%20its%20manifesto%2C%20just%20as%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes%20have%20got%20the%20reservation%2C%20similarly%2C%20Muslims%20will%20also%20be%20given%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSP%20had%20said%20that%20it%20would%20even%20change%20the%20Constitution%20for%20this.%20SP%20had%20announced%20that%2015%20per%20cent%20reservation%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Muslims%20in%20police%20and%20PAC%20also.%20How%20these%20people%20were%20bent%20on%20snatching%20away%20the%20rights%20of%20SC-ST-OBC%20to%20please%20their%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20Mirzapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20emphasized%20that%20he%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716711720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6g443uv4_narendra-modi-pti_625x300_25_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw