20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20soon%20joined%20by%20fire%20department%20officials%20and%20the%20police.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Sewa%20Dal%20alleged%20the%20hospital%20staff%20ran%20away%20soon%20after%20the%20building%20caught%20fire.%20Another%20resident%2C%20Mukesh%20Bansal%2C%20alleged%20an%20illegal%20oxygen%20refilling%20cylinder%20work%20was%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20complained%20about%20it%20to%20the%20local%20councillor%20as%20well.%20But%20nothing%20was%20done.%20It%20was%20all%20happening%20under%20the%20nose%20of%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bansal%20alleged.%20He%20said%20he%20used%20to%20live%20next%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20work%20of%20refilling%20cylinders%2C%20he%20shifted%20to%20the%20next%20lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Fire%20Services%20said%20the%20blaze%20broke%20out%20at%2011.30%20pm%20on%20Saturday%20and%20soon%20spread%20to%20two%20other%20adjacent%20buildings.%20Sixteen%20fire%20trucks%20came%20to%20douse%20the%20blaze%2C%20Divisional%20Fire%20Officer%20Rajendra%20Atwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxygen%20cylinders%20kept%20in%20the%20two-storey%20building%20exploded%20due%20to%20which%20the%20adjacent%20buildings%20were%20damaged%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20fire%20official%20said%20two%20boutiques%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20IndusInd%20Bank%20operating%20from%20an%20adjacent%20building%20and%20a%20shop%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20were%20also%20damaged%20besides%20an%20ambulance%20and%20a%20scooty%20parked%20outside%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondoling%20the%20death%20of%20the%20children%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20prayed%20for%20strength%20to%20the%20bereaved%20parents.%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20those%20responsible%20for%20negligence%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20fire%20tragedy%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Delhi%20is%20heart-rending.%20%26quot%3BMy%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20bereaved%20families%20in%20this%20incredibly%20difficult%20time.%20I%20pray%20that%20those%20injured%20recover%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716711420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F8sbvsaao_delhi-hospital-fire_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fin-daring-act-how-locals-ran-inside-burning-delhi-hospital-to-save-babies-5748751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20who%20saw%20a%20huge%20fire%20engulf%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20Delhi%20scaled%20the%20compound%20wall%2C%20and%20climbed%20from%20the%20rear%20side%20of%20the%20building%20to%20rescue%20newborns%2C%20eyewitnesses%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fin-daring-act-how-locals-ran-inside-burning-delhi-hospital-to-save-babies-5748751%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fin-daring-act-how-locals-ran-inside-burning-delhi-hospital-to-save-babies-5748751%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fin-daring-act-how-locals-ran-inside-burning-delhi-hospital-to-save-babies-5748751%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chun%20Woo-hee%20on%20his%20role%20in%20'The%208%20Show'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716711390000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110436727%2Cimgsize-15886.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fchun-woo-hee-opens-up-about-tackling-complex-role-in-the-8-show-after-replacing-iu-i-hope-people-wont-hate-her-too-much%2Farticleshow%2F110436769.cms%22%2C%