%20to%20be%20the%20domain%20name%20assigned%20to%20the%20island%2C%20similar%20to%20%26quot%3B.jp%26quot%3B%20for%20Japan%20and%20%26quot%3B.fr%26quot%3B%20for%20France.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnguilla's%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20surged%20from%20144%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20354%2C000%20in%202023%2C%20generating%20over%2020%25%20of%20the%20government's%20total%20revenue%20for%20the%20year.%20Find%20out%20in%20our%20Country%20Focus%20how%20this%20helps%20diversify%20the%20economy%2C%20making%20it%20more%20resilient%20to%20shocks.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FULk3V6oVyb%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FULk3V6oVyb%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqgMdCa4aYo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqgMdCa4aYo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IMF%20(%40IMFNews)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIMFNews%2Fstatus%2F1794058295277416941%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FNews%2FArticles%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fcf-an-ai-powered-boost-to-anguillas-revenues%5C%22%3Ethe%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%20that%20Anguilla's%20country%20code%20%E2%80%9C.ai%E2%80%9D%20has%20become%20a%20favourite%20among%20technology%20companies%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20revealed%20that%20since%20the%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20registrations%20for%20the%20.ai%20domain%20name%20have%20surged%20dramatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20registrations%20soared%20from%20144%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20354%2C000%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(AI)%20have%20also%20generated%20an%20unusual%20boom%20in%20Anguilla%2C%20a%20British%20overseas%20territory%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Caribbean%20Currency%20Union%2C%20whose%20.ai%20country-code%20internet%20domain%20has%20become%20a%20favourite%20among%20technology%20companies%20across%20the%20world.%20Since%20the%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%20November%202022%2C%20registrations%20of%20.ai%20domain%20names%20have%20skyrocketed%E2%80%94surging%20from%20144%2C000%20registrations%20in%202022%20to%20354%2C000%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20revenue%20being%20generated%2C%20the%20IMF%20revealed%20that%20last%20year%20%E2%80%9C.ai%20domain%20registrations%20generated%20EC%2487%20million.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20this%20is%2020%20per%20cent%20more%20than%20the%20Anguillan%20government's%20total%20revenue%20generation%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%20alone%2C%20this%20surge%20in%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20generated%20EC%2487%20million%20in%20revenue%20(approximately%20%2432%20million)%E2%80%94just%20over%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20government's%20total%20revenue%20for%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20marks%20a%20dramatic%20increase%20from%20previous%20years%20when%20revenue%20from%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20hovered%20around%205%20per%20cent.%20Looking%20ahead%2C%20the%20government%20expects%20revenue%20from%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20to%20stabilize%20at%20around%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20government%20revenue%2C%20as%20the%20initial%20rush%20of%20registrations%20gradually%20slows.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20noted%20that%20Anguilla%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20tourism%20activities%20that%20account%20for%2037%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20GDP.%C2%A0%20The%20growing%20trend%20of%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20is%20now%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20diversifying%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716710820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http