the%20bus%2C%20and%20couldn't%20reach%20the%20classroom.%20I%20told%20him%20to%20immediately%20drop%20her%20home%2C%20but%20he%20didn't.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20I%20called%20her%20teacher%20that%20she%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident.%20We%20rushed%20to%20the%20school%20by%208.15%20am%2C%20but%20my%20daughter%20hadn't%20reached%20the%20classroom%20or%20school%20yet%2C''%20the%20girl's%20mother%20recalled%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20said%20her%20head%20banged%20against%20the%20front%20seat.%20And%20as%20she%20woke%20up%2C%20there%20were%20all%20the%20big%20students%2C%20i.e.%2C%20boys%20and%20senior%20students%20of%20the%20second%20trip.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20she%20started%20crying%20that%20the%20conductor%20realised%20she%20was%20left%20inside%20and%20then%20called%20me%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl's%20parents%20have%20now%20withdrawn%20her%20from%20the%20school%20and%20complained%20to%20the%20local%20authorities%2C%20complaining%20that%20the%20staff%20downplayed%20it%20as%20a%20minor%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20find%20the%20heart%20to%20send%20her%20to%20school%20until%20she%20is%20a%20bit%20older%20to%20look%20after%20herself.%20I%20have%20studied%20in%20the%20same%20school%2C%20but%20I%20never%20expected%20my%20daughter%20to%20be%20treated%20this%20way.%20Our%20trust%20has%20been%20broken.%20We%20are%20lucky%20to%20get%20our%20child%20alive%3B%20I%20pray%20no%20other%20parents%20and%20child%20undergo%20such%20a%20miserable%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20further%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20such%20cases%20of%20carelessness%20wherein%20children%20have%20suffocated%20to%20death%20or%20fell%20ill%20after%20being%20left%20behind%20in%20school%20buses%20or%20private%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716710280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024