22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20praised%20Rikant%20Pittie%2C%20Co-founder%20of%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20how%20Digital%20India%20initiatives%20have%20fostered%20a%20thriving%20Indian%20startup%20ecosystem%20and%20are%20poised%20to%20accelerate%20the%20Viksit%20Bharat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stop%20Commercial%20Sale%20Of%20Human%20Milk%2C%20Warns%20Food%20Safety%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20food%20regulator%20has%20warned%20against%20the%20unauthorized%20commercialization%20of%20human%20milk%2C%20stating%20that%20its%20rules%20do%20not%20permit%20the%20sale%20of%20such%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20advisory%20dated%20May%2024%2C%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%20has%20advised%20all%20activities%20related%20to%20human%20milk%20sales%20to%20be%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFSSAI%20has%20not%20permitted%20the%20processing%20and%2For%20selling%20of%20human%20milk%20under%20FSS%20Act%2C%202006%20and%20rules%2Fregulations%20made%20there%20under.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20advised%20that%20all%20such%20activities%20related%20to%20the%20commercialization%20of%20human%20milk%20and%20its%20products%20should%20be%20immediately%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20violation%20of%20the%20rules%20will%20lead%20to%20action%20against%20the%20food%20business%20operators%20(FBOs)%2C%20the%20FSSAI%20said%20in%20its%20advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FSSAI%2C%20which%20regulates%20the%20manufacturing%20and%20sale%20of%20food%20items%20in%20the%20country%2C%20has%20also%20called%20on%20state%20and%20central%20licensing%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20licenses%20are%20not%20given%20to%20food%20businesses%20involved%20in%20processing%20or%20selling%20human%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20sale%20of%20human%20milk%20has%20boomed%20with%20milk%20banks%20set%20up%20as%20non-profits%20collecting%20milk%20from%20lactating%20mothers%20and%20selling%20them%20at%20a%20profit.%20A%20simple%20Google%20search%20shows%20the%20numerous%20options%20one%20has%20to%20buy%20such%20products%20online%2C%20including%20Instagram%20handles%20and%20milk%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilk%20banks%20usually%20process%20the%20milk%20collected%20from%20healthy%20donors%20(lactating%20mothers)%20and%20check%20contamination%20and%20nutrient%20contents%20before%20freezing%20and%20storing%20them.%20Most%20milk%20banks%2C%20which%20are%20attached%20to%20government%20hospitals%2C%20usually%20provide%20it%20for%20free%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Times%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716709620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Fbaby-milk-nutrition-istock_650x400_81480677641.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffood-safety-body-cracks-down-on-commercial-sale-of-human-milk-5748353%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20country's%20food%20regulator%20has%20warned%20against%20the%20unauthorized%20commercialization%20of%20human%20milk%2C%20stating%20that%20its%20rules%20do%20not%20permit%20the%20sale%20of%20such%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffood-safety-body-cracks-down-on-commercial-sale-of-human-milk-5748353%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffood-safety-body-cracks-down-on-commercial-sale-of-human-milk-5748353%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffood-safety-body-cracks-down-on-commercial-sale-of-human-milk-5748353%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indresh%20defends%20Sharmin%2C%20predicts%20her%20bright%20future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716709590