d%20when%20a%20fore%20tore%20through%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20eastern%20Delhi%20late%20last%20night.%20The%20owner%20of%20the%20hospital%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20run%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20fled%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20within%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwelve%20newborn%20babies%20were%20rescued%20from%20the%20hospital%20with%20the%20help%20of%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Shahdara)%20Surendra%20Choudhary%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20but%20adding%20that%20when%20they%20reached%20medical%20attention%2C%20seven%20were%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%2C%20which%20erupted%20around%2011.32%20pm%2C%20quickly%20intensified%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20numerous%20oxygen%20cylinders%20that%20began%20to%20explode%2C%20spreading%20the%20blaze%20further%20and%20causing%20extensive%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20received%20the%20call%20at%2011.32%20pm%20and%20initially%20dispatched%20seven%20fire%20trucks%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20additional%20fourteen.%20There%20were%204-5%20explosions%20that%20significantly%20worsened%20the%20fire%2C%20with%20oxygen%20cylinders%20being%20hurled%20as%20far%20as%2050%20meters%20away.%20The%20building%2C%20which%20was%20ground%20plus%20three%20stories%20high%2C%20housed%20the%20children%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20and%20a%20storage%20area%20on%20the%20second.%20The%20fire%20spread%20to%20adjacent%20floors%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Atul%20Garg%2C%20Chief%20Fire%20Officer%20told%20NDTV%20detailing%20the%20harrowing%20events%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirefighters%20battled%20the%20inferno%20for%20three%20hours%2C%20during%20which%20time%20the%20challenges%20of%20locating%20and%20rescuing%20the%20infants%20added%20to%20the%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20know%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20children%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garg%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20initial%20cause%20of%20the%20fire%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20an%20electrical%20pole%20igniting%2C%20which%20then%20set%20fire%20to%20a%20parked%20vehicle%2C%20eventually%20causing%20the%20oxygen%20cylinders%20to%20catch%20fire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Garg%20also%20noted%20that%20while%20the%20building%20had%20reportedly%20acquired%20a%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%2C%20the%20fire%20department%20had%20no%20records%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20verifying%20the%20NOC.%20If%20it's%20found%20lacking%2C%20we%20will%20recommend%20the%20building's%20closure.%20An%20investigation%20is%20underway%20to%20determine%20if%20proper%20firefighting%20measures%20were%20in%20place%2C%20but%20it's%20difficult%20to%20assess%20right%20now%20as%20the%20building%20is%20completely%20gutted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20Naveen%20Kichi%2C%20fled%20before%20the%20police%20reached%20his%20home.%20Cops%20believe%20that%20he%20may%20be%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20have%20formed%20a%20team%20to%20find%20and%20arrest%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20whoever%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20accident%20will%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20causes%20of%20the%20incident%20are%20being%20investigated%20and%20whoever%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20negligence%20will%20not%20be%20spared%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi's%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716708720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F799ausr4_delhi-fire_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Felectrical-pole-oxygen-cylinders-why-fire-at-delhi-childrens-hospital-spread-5748512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20newborns%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20fore%20tore%20through%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20eastern%20Delhi%20late%20last%20night.%20The%20owner%20of%20the%20hospital%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20run%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20fled%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20within%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Felectrical-pole-oxygen-cylinders-why-fire-at-delhi-childrens-hospital-spread-5748512%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Felectrical-pole-oxygen-cylinders-why-fire-at-delhi-childrens-hospital-spread-5748512%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Felectrical-pole-oxygen-cylinders-why-fire-at-delhi-childrens-hospital-spread-5748512%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajnath%20Singh's%20'Back%20Off'%20Reply%20To%20Opposition%20Over%20Agnipath%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20not%20useful%2C%20and%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20government's%20stand%20that%20the%20four-year%20enlistment%20programme%20will%20benefit%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20young%2C%20employable%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20fully%20confident%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20successful%20and%20will%20remain%20so.%20One%20of%20the%20factors%20behind%20starting%20this%20scheme%20is%20to%20bring%20more%20young%20people%20into%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%2C%20selected%20candidates%20are%20enrolled%20as%20Agniveers%20for%20a%20four-year%20period.%20On%20completion%20of%20programme%2C%20Agniveers%20will%20return%20to%20the%20society%20as%20disciplined%2C%20dynamic%2C%20motivated%20and%20skilled%20workforce%20for%20employment%20in%20other%20sectors%20to%20pursue%20their%20career%20in%20a%20job%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%20Of%20these%2C%20up%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20Agniveers%20will%20be%20enrolled%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20as%20regular%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20factor%20is%20we%20should%20strive%20to%20have%20a%20section%20of%20the%20population%20disciplined%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Agniveers.%20When%20needed%2C%20they%20will%20have%20the%20right%20skills%20to%20help%20out%20in%20the%20frontline%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20crime%20to%20prepare%20Agniveers%20to%20be%20disciplined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Opposition's%20allegations%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20would%20harm%20the%20future%20of%20young%20adults%20who%20are%20just%20entering%20the%20workforce%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20the%20youths%20that%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20play%20with%20their%20future.%20An%20Agniveer%20is%20eligible%20from%2018%20years%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20so%20for%20four%20years.%20They%20will%20learn%20new%20skills%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20four%20years%20will%20have%20a%20few%20lakh%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20of%20them%20wants%20to%20find%20a%20job%2C%20they%20can.%20If%20any%20of%20them%20wants%20to%20enter%20the%20paramilitary%20forces%2C%20they%20can.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20services%2C%20of%20course%20they%20can.%20We%20have%20even%20kept%20reservations%20for%20them.%20It's%20not%20like%20anyone%20can%20ignore%20them.%20The%20private%20sector%20also%20wants%20to%20hire%20Agniveers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20play%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20young%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20strongly%20criticised%20the%20Opposition%20for%20dragging%20the%20military%20into%20an%20election%20campaign%20issue.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Opposition)%20has%20only%20one%20agenda%20-%20to%20confuse%20citizens.%20They%20should%20not%20play%20politics%20over%20Agniveers%20and%20the%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20contested%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%20constituency%20this%20time%20again.%20He%20had%20won%20from%20there%20twice.%20Lucknow%20is%20a%20prestigious%20seat%20previously%20represented%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%202019%2C%20with%20an%20even%20larger%20seat%20share%20than%20in%202014.%20Mr%20Singh%20remained%20one%20of%20the%20key%20members%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20cabinet%20and%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Defence%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20the%20spirit%20of%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20'Aatmanirbhar%20Bharat'%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20banned%20the%20import%20of%20101%20defence-related%20items%20in%202020.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20108%20military%20weapons%20and%20systems%2C%20including%20next-generation%20corvettes%2C%20airborne%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20tank%20engines%20and%20radars%20would%20be%20entirely%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716708600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbq5oplh8_rajnath-singh-ndtv_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-rajnath-singhs-back-off-reply-to-opposition-on-playing-politics-over-agnipath-scheme-5748197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20not%20useful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-rajnath-singhs-back-off-reply-to-opposition-on-playing-politics-over-agnipath-scheme-5748197%22%