here%20the%20Kolkata%20side%20has%20finished%20among%20the%20bottom%20teams%20in%20the%20T20%20league%2C%20what%20has%20pinched%20SRK%20the%20most%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20costume%20of%20his%20team%20was%20questioned%20during%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Star%20Sports%2C%20the%20broadcaster%20of%20IPL%202024%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20called%20his%20team%20the%20'nicest%20in%20the%20world'%20while%20also%20opening%20up%20on%20certain%20moments%20which%20made%20him%20'sad'%20as%20an%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20the%20nicest%20set%20of%20team%20in%20the%20world%20and%20we%20kept%20on%20losing%20only%20again%20and%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20SRK%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20remember%2C%20which%20was%20the%20saddest%20moment%2C%20kisi%20ne%20mujhe%20aise%20bola%20'inka%20costume%20hi%20achha%20hai%2C%20inka%20game%20play%20to%20achhai%20hai%20hi%20nahi'%20(someday%20said%20to%20me%20'only%20their%20playing%20kit%20is%20nice%2C%20not%20their%20game').%20I%20remember%20some%20expert%20talking%20this.%20It%20used%20to%20hurt.%20To%20come%20back%20with%20GG%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20do%20this%20was%20outstanding.%20It%20taught%20us%20how%20to%20lose%20but%20never%20be%20losers%20and%20never%20give%20up%20hope.%20Sports%20teaches%20you%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20Rukh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEXCLUSIVE%20CHAT%20with%20SRK%3A%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20recounts%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20rise%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20with%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20leading%20them%20to%20two%20titles!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20this%20interview%20with%20Star%20Sports%2C%20Shahrukh%20Khan%20talks%20about%20having%20the%20nicest%20set%20of%20team