h%20three%20dots%20painting')%20as%20a%20search%20term%20led%20us%20to%20a%202017%20blog%20post%20with%20the%20same%20image.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20identified%20the%20image%20as%20a%201932%20painting%20titled%20'Madonna%20Oriflamma'%20by%20one%20Nikolai%20Roerich.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20geometrical%20art%20was%20Roerich's%20creation%2C%20which%20he%20called%20the%20'Banner%20of%20peace'%2C%20elaborating%20on%20the%20symbolism%20of%20the%20banner.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20looked%20up%20the%20name%20of%20the%20painting%20and%20found%20it%20on%20several%20websites%20across%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20results%20included%20the%20painting's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wikiart.org%2Fen%2Fnicholas-roerich%2Fmadonna-oriflamma-1932%5C%22%3EWikiArt%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20updated%20in%202013%2C%20which%20mentioned%20that%20the%20art%20was%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Nicholas%20Roerich%20Museum%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fro6gvhc_madonna-oriflamma_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20museum's%20Facebook%20page%20also%20shared%20the%20painting's%20photograph%20in%202021%2C%20discussing%20its%20meaning%20and%20symbolism.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMoreover%2C%20Roerich's%20website%20also%20carries%20a%20visual%20of%20the%20painting%20with%20details%20about%20its%20medium%20and%20dimensions%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20has%20been%20on%20loan%20to%20the%20museum%20since%201960.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20and%20printed%20versions%20of%20the%20painting%20are%20also%20easily%20available%20for%20purchase%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20as%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fmeidasi-Paintings-Oriflamma%25EF%25BC%258CArt-Decoratives-20x30inch%2Fdp%2FB0CXN67KX2%3Fth%3D1%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fin-en%2Flisting%2F1723188261%2Fnicholas-roerich-madonna-oriflamma-and%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meisterdrucke.ie%2Ffine-art-prints%2FNicholas-Roerich%2F823071%2FMadonna-Oriflamma%252C-1932.html%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20painting%20seen%20in%20Rahul%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20photo%20is%20not%20one%20of%20Jesus%20Christ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fwebqoof%2Frahul-gandhi-sonia-gandhi-jesus-picture-fact-check%5C%22%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716694260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fgtngssu_sonia-rahul-fact-check_625x300_25_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-painting-behind-sonia-gandhi-rahul-not-of-jesus-christ-5745800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20shared%20a%20selfie%20of%20him%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20having%20voted%20during%20the%20sixth%20phase%20of%20polling%20for%20the%20ongoing%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20photo%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-painting-behind-sonia-gandhi-rahul-not-of-jesus-christ-5745800%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-painting-behind-sonia-gandhi-rahul-not-of-jesus-christ-5745800%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A