%20telemedical%20consultancy%20calls%20per%20day%20and%20charges%20Rs%2090%20for%20a%20consultation%20with%20the%20expert%20whereas%20Rs%20150%20for%20a%20field%20visit%2C%20which%20Manish%20says%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20market%20which%20charges%20Rs%20300-500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20has%20also%20designed%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20tags%20to%20monitor%20and%20trace%20the%20health%2C%20location%2C%20and%20movement%20of%20livestock.%20It%20also%20stores%20prescriptions%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260896%2Fodisha-balaram-sahu-free-doctor-treatment-cow-cattle-diseases-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisease%20history%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%20Of%20this%2C%20more%20than%201.7%20lakh%20are%20directly%20benefitting%20through%20teleconsultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20major%20health%20issues%20in%20livestock%20were%20productivity%20and%20difficulties%20in%20pregnancies%20owing%20to%20malnutrition.%20We%20provide%20herbal%20treatment%20that%20boosts%20suitable%20ovulation%20period%20in%20cattle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350780%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVerdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20bovines%20usually%20conceive%20in%2037%20to%2040%20months%20if%20it%20is%20malnourished%20but%20when%20you%20provide%20good%20nutrition%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20conceive%20in%2022%20to%2027%20months.%20This%20gives%20farmers%20an%20extra%20cycle%20for%20gestation%20before%20the%20bovine%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20calving.%20Depending%20on%20the%20breed%2C%20they%20earn%20an%20extra%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20to%203%20lakh%20annually%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Manish%20points%20out%20that%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20main%20revenue%20is%20generated%20through%20cattle%20commerce%2C%20genetics%20care%2C%20and%20sales%20through%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274439%2Fagritech-startup-e-feed-helps-cattle-farmers-increase-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20health%20supplements%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Currently%2C%20his%20annual%20revenue%20stands%20at%20Rs%208.72%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20lives%20revolve%20around%20livestock%20and%20we%20have%20proved%20that%20we%20are%20not%20a%20charitable%20organisation.%20We%20are%20a%20viable%20profitable%20business.%20This%20achievement%20is%20too%20big%20for%20a%20PhD%20dropout%20and%20a%20farmer%20like%20me%2C%