Health%20and%20Neurosciences)%2C%20she%20shares%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20therapy%20for%20the%20same.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20therapy%20sessions%20and%20difficulty%20in%20communicating%20with%20her%20little%20one%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20young%20mother%2C%20which%20subsequently%20led%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20up%20gardening%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gardening%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Sushma%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-500x666.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-768x1023.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-1153x1536.jpeg%201153w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349841%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGardening%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Sushma.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20trip%20home%20to%20Visakhapatnam%20in%202018%2C%20Sushma%20remembered%20her%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20advice%20and%20got%20back%20a%20money%20plant-cutting%20to%20start%20her%20gardening%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20my%20relatives%20are%20farmers%20and%20also%20grow%20plants%20at%20home.%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20gardening%20tips%20and%20started%20my%20journey%20%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETending%20to%20the%20money%20plant%20gave%20the%20gardener%20the%20confidence%20to%20try%20growing%20more%20plants.%20She%20ventured%20into%20growing%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20which%20she%20would%20feed%20her%20son%20daily.%20Later%2C%20she%20added%20more%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%20and%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20vegetables%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20easy%2C%20she%20discovered%2C%20as%20she%20encountered%20many%20failures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20one%20harvest%20of%20tomatoes%20but%20the%20next%20one%20would%20fail.%20I%20referred%20to%20several%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20learn%20the%20ropes%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20experience%20is%20the%20biggest%20teacher.%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20when%20and%20how%20often%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20give%20fertiliser.%20How%20much%20direct%20sunlight%20should%20be%20given%20was%20also%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20she%20learnt%20that%20it%20was%20ideal%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20early%20morning%2C%20between%207%20to%208%20am%2C%20the%20best%20time%20to%20do%20pest%20control%20was%20either%20before%206%20am%20or%20after%206%20pm%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20generally%20need%20more%20water.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20each%20vegetable%2C%20flower%20and%20fruit%20was%20different%2C%20and%20she%20would%20have%20to%20work%20her%20way%20around%20that%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGardening%20as%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20her%20plants%20started%20growing%20beautifully.%20Seeing%20her%20vegetables%20thrive%20gave%20her%20the%20confidence%20to%20start%20growing%20fruits.%20She%20also%20had%20a%20more%20important%20motive%20%E2%80%93%20encouraging%20her%20son%20to%20eat%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sushma%20(%40glitters.of.nature)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20guava%2C%20she%20today%20grows%20over%2070%20fruit%20trees%2C%20including%20mango%2C%20dragon%20fruit%2C%20custard%20apple%2C%20banana%2C%20papaya%2C%20strawberry.%20The%20trick%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20to%20buy%20grafted%20fruit%20plants%2C%20which%20will%20give%20you%20a%20better%20yield%20compared%20to%20seeds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20learnt%20this%20after%20she%20tried%20growing%20lemon%20and%20mango%20using%20seeds.%20The%20lemon%20tree%20bore%20fruit%20after%20five%20years%2C%20while%20she%E2%80%99s%20still%20waiting%20for%20that%20mango%20tree%20to%20bear%20fruit!%20Using%20grafted%20fruit%20plants%2C%20she%20has%20managed%20to%20grow%20over%20six%20varieties%20of%20mango.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20flowers%20will%20drop%20as%20the%20plant%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20fruit.%20Remove%20the%20flowers%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20plant.%20Typically%2C%20you%20will%20not%20get%20any%20fruits%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20maybe%20two%20in%20the%20second%2C%20five%20to%20six%20in%20the%20third%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20gardener.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushma%20grows%20all%20her%20fruits%20in%2010-16%20inch%20pots%20on%20her%20terrace%2C%20as%20she%20stays%20in%20a%20rented%20apartment%20and%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20for%20her%20to%20transport%20them%2C%20should%20the%20need%20arise.%20She%20would%20get%20a%20much%20better%20yield%20with%20bigger%20pots%2C%20she%20asserts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident%20is%20extremely%20satisfied%20with%20the%20yield%20that%20her%20terrace%20garden%20produces.%20With%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%20vegetables%20and%2070%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20her%20family%20eats%20what%20they%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20happy%20today%20as%20I%20found%20my%20passion%20in%20gardening.%20It%20gives%20me%20immense%20satisfaction.%20Th