ed-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20Jaipur%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Geeta%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20Soda%20in%202020.%20The%20dearth%20of%20work%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20continue.%20When%20she%20reached%20the%20village%2C%20news%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20college%20taking%20in%20applicants%20reached%20her.%20One%20conversation%20with%20Rajawat%20later%2C%20Geeta%20was%20convinced%20this%20was%20the%20place%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChhavi%20ma%E2%80%99am%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20my%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education).%20Everyone%20around%20me%20was%20keen%20to%20see%20me%20study.%20I%20began%20noticing%20how%20the%20village%20mindset%20had%20evolved.%E2%80%9D%20Geeta%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20the%20two-year%20course%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20at%20the%20village%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimparting%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2010-year-olds%20is%20her%20first%20priority%2C%20another%20goal%20is%20to%20dispel%20stereotypes%20that%20force%20women%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20dreams.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20550%20students%20at%20the%20college.%20They%20are%20engaged%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20courses%20offered%20here%3A%20BEd%20(Bachelor%20of%20Education)%2C%20a%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education)%2C%20and%20a%20BA%20(Bachelor%20of%20Arts)%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201288px)%20100vw%2C%201288px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads